WEBVTT

00:08:58.924 --> 00:09:01.634
What rights of publicity
or privacy do they have?

00:09:01.658 --> 00:09:03.235
Did they get paid?

00:09:03.259 --> 00:09:04.425
Should they get paid?

00:09:04.449 --> 00:09:06.100
Should they share in the profit?

00:09:06.124 --> 00:09:08.250
This is a for-profit game.

00:09:08.274 --> 00:09:10.441
Did they sign talent waivers?

00:09:10.465 --> 00:09:13.075
I have to use these
when I'm working with NGOs

00:09:13.099 --> 00:09:16.331
and documentary filmmakers
here in the States.

00:09:16.355 --> 00:09:19.768
In the States, we take our right
to privacy and publicity

00:09:19.792 --> 00:09:21.319
very seriously.

00:09:21.343 --> 00:09:24.589
So what is it about getting
on a long-haul flight

00:09:24.613 --> 00:09:26.779
that makes these rights vaporize?

00:09:27.176 --> 00:09:30.049
I don't want to just pick on our friends
in the gaming arts;